      <title>英国央行降息并暗示谨慎前行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bank-of-england-gives-hawkish-warning-as-it-cuts-rates-to-4-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行官员一致决定将利率降至19个月低点，其中两位官员支持大幅降息50个基点，促使市场加大对进一步宽松政策的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bank-of-england-gives-hawkish-warning-as-it-cuts-rates-to-4-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 12:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cemex 预计 2024 年美国需求将回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cemex-sees-recovery-in-us-demand-after-cement-sales-drop-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥 Cemex SAB 预计，今年其水泥在其最大市场美国的需求将有所改善，此前其 2024 年的水泥销量下降导致其销售下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cemex-sees-recovery-in-us-demand-after-cement-sales-drop-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 11:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威 1.8 万亿美元基金聚焦 ESG 领域，裁减 49 家公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/norway-1-8-trillion-fund-quit-49-companies-for-esg-risk-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，挪威1.8万亿美元的主权财富基金根据可持续性评估从49家公司撤资，低于前年的86家。尽管环境、社会和治理报告遭到广泛反对，该基金仍将重点放在ESG上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/norway-1-8-trillion-fund-quit-49-companies-for-esg-risk-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:48:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收益缓解贸易担忧，欧洲股市创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/european-stocks-surpass-closing-record-on-earnings-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，欧洲股市创下历史新高，受美国贸易不确定性加剧之际企业盈利仍保持弹性的乐观情绪推动。英国央行降息后，英国股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/european-stocks-surpass-closing-record-on-earnings-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:12:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
